{"title":"Leetcode第30题：串联所有单词的子串","slug":"2019101001","date":"2019-10-10T14:12:23.000Z","updated":"2019-10-10T14:12:31.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2019101001.json","excerpt":"题目给定一个字符串 s 和一些长度相同的单词 words。找出 s 中恰好可以由 words 中所有单词串联形成的子串的起始位置。","covers":["https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc1e95a8c314a459592bd2eddddab789eB.png","https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf7cd5142614a4411838300ab4dcef118d.png"],"content":"<h2 id=\"题目\"><a href=\"#题目\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目\"></a>题目</h2><p>给定一个字符串 s 和一些长度相同的单词 words。找出 s 中恰好可以由 words 中所有单词串联形成的子串的起始位置。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<p>注意子串要与 words 中的单词完全匹配，中间不能有其他字符，但不需要考虑 words 中单词串联的顺序。<br><strong>示例1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong><br>  s = “barfoothefoobarman”,<br>  words = [“foo”,”bar”]<br><strong>输出：</strong>[0,9]<br><strong>解释：</strong><br>从索引 0 和 9 开始的子串分别是 “barfoor” 和 “foobar” 。<br>输出的顺序不重要, [9,0] 也是有效答案。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong><br>  s = “wordgoodgoodgoodbestword”,<br>  words = [“word”,”good”,”best”,”word”]<br><strong>输出：</strong>[]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"class\"><span class=\"keyword\">class</span> <span class=\"title\">Solution</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    String s;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    List&lt;String&gt; words;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> List&lt;Integer&gt; <span class=\"title\">findSubstring</span><span class=\"params\">(String s, String[] words)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        List&lt;Integer&gt; result=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(words==<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>||words.length==<span class=\"number\">0</span>||words[<span class=\"number\">0</span>].equals(<span class=\"string\">&quot;&quot;</span>))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> tmplen=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(String tmp:words)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            tmplen+=tmp.length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;i&lt;s.length();i++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(String tmp:words)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.add(tmp);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">boolean</span> flag=<span class=\"keyword\">true</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">int</span> baseLen=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(s.substring(i).length()&gt;=tmplen)</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">while</span>(flag)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">for</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> j=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;j&lt;<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.size();j++)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>((i+baseLen+<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.get(j).length()&lt;=s.length())&amp;&amp;(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.get(j).equals(s.substring(i+baseLen,i+baseLen+<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.get(j).length()))))&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            baseLen+=<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.get(j).length();</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            <span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.remove(j);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            <span class=\"keyword\">break</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(j+<span class=\"number\">1</span>==<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.size())&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                            flag=<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.size()==<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                        flag=<span class=\"keyword\">false</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"keyword\">if</span>(<span class=\"keyword\">this</span>.words.size()==<span class=\"number\">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                    result.add(i);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> result;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h3 id=\"运行结果\"><a href=\"#运行结果\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"运行结果\"></a>运行结果</h3><p><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hc1e95a8c314a459592bd2eddddab789eB.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"总结\"><a href=\"#总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"总结\"></a>总结</h2><p>怎么说呢。。。10月2号一直到现在一直没有做这道题一个是这道题确实有难度，并且国庆嘛，回家啦，就一直挺忙的，一直没时间做，今天算是回归了正轨，就打算试一试，这道题确实很有挑战性，2个多小时9次Fail我差点就想放弃了！一开始使用的方法是递归法，动态的将全部words全排列一个一个对比，但是Fail时看了测试用例后就发现递归的话时间根本不够啊，于是最后打破了之前的思想，将所有的word存在一个临时列表里，然后for循环s字符串，裁取第i位到最后一位，如果第i位开始和某一个word是一样的，继续裁去掉该word，并在列表里移除掉该word，如果所有的word都可以不分先后的被移除，则将i存到result中。以此类推，即可AC。^_^<br><img src=\"https://ae01.alicdn.com/kf/Hf7cd5142614a4411838300ab4dcef118d.png\"></p>\n","more":"<p>注意子串要与 words 中的单词完全匹配，中间不能有其他字符，但不需要考虑 words 中单词串联的顺序。<br><strong>示例1：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong><br>  s = “barfoothefoobarman”,<br>  words = [“foo”,”bar”]<br><strong>输出：</strong>[0,9]<br><strong>解释：</strong><br>从索引 0 和 9 开始的子串分别是 “barfoor” 和 “foobar” 。<br>输出的顺序不重要, [9,0] 也是有效答案。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>示例2：</strong></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>输入：</strong><br>  s = “wordgoodgoodgoodbestword”,<br>  words = [“word”,”good”,”best”,”word”]<br><strong>输出：</strong>[]</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h2><figure class=\"highlight java\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><s